('Hoya Hoya no Mi', 'Puff-Puff Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/9/97/Hoya_Hoya_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20210208063127', 'allows the user to summon a genie from their body, making the user a Lamp Human (ランプ人間 Ranpu Ningen).', null, 'Charlotte Daifuku', null, 1),

('Netsu Netsu no Mi', 'Heat-Heat Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/c/c5/Netsu_Netsu_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20210208063018', 'The user is capable of heating parts of their body to temperatures greater than most people can withstand. This greatly aids them in a confrontation. They can transfer the heat to other objects, most notably the opponents'' weapons, making them too hot to wield. This transfer of heat can even happen without physical contact, as demonstrated when Oven seemingly projected heat energy to set a gun ablaze.', null, 'Charlotte Oven', null, 1),

