('Hebi Hebi no Mi, Model: Yamata no Orochi', 'Snake-Snake Fruit, Model: Yamata-no-Orochi', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/3/3e/Hebi_Hebi_no_Mi%2C_Model_Yamata_no_Orochi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20210307032049', 'allows the user to transform into a hybrid and full version of the Yamata no Orochi, an eight-headed snake or dragon in Japanese mythology.', null, null, 'Kurozumi Orochi', 4),

