('Inu Inu no Mi, Model: Bake-danuki', 'Dog-Dog Fruit, Model: Bake-danuki', false, 'One Piece: Unlimited World Red', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/0/05/Inu_Inu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Bake-danuki_Infobox.png/revision/latest?cb=20130929013736', 'gives the user the specific traits of the mythical raccoon dog in which it can transform ordinary leaves into anything else, from objects to other people and entire environments.', null, 'Patrick Redfield''s pen: Pato', null, 4),

('Inu Inu no Mi, Model: Jackal', 'Dog-Dog Fruit, Model: Jackal', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/4f/Inu_Inu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Jackal_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20130919152838', 'enables the eater to become a large, black jackal at will, granting an increase in physical strength, speed, and senses.', null, 'Chaka', null, 2),

('Inu Inu no Mi, Model: Dachshund', 'Mutt-Mutt Fruit, Model: Dachshund', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/d0/Inu_Inu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Dachshund_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20200625092631', 'allows its user to transform into a dachshund hybrid and a full dachshund at will.', null, 'Mr.4''s bazooka, Lassoo', null, 2),

('Inu Inu no Mi, Model: Wolf', 'Mutt-Mutt Fruit, Model: Wolf', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/e/e1/Full-Beast_Form_of_Jabra%27s_fruit.png/revision/latest?cb=20211029235543', 'user gains more physical strength in their hybrid and full wolf forms, equivalent to that of a real wolf and more.', null, 'Jabra', null, 2), 

