('Inu Inu no Mi, Model: Kyubi no Kitsune', 'Dog-Dog Fruit, Model: Nine Tailed Fox', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/4d/Inu_Inu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Kyubi_no_Kitsune_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20210717170215', 'allows the user to transform into a nine-tailed fox.', null, 'Catarina Devon', null, 4),

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Allosaurus', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit. Model: Allosaurus', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/a3/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Allosaurus_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220301122130', 'allows the user to transform into an allosaurus, a large and powerful theropod dinosaur from the prehistoric era, as a carnivorous Ancient Zoan the fruit grants them features much better suited for close combat than basic Zoans such as sharp teeth and claws. As is the case with every other Zoan ability, the user can also become a human-animal hybrid at will.', null, 'X Drake', null, 3),

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Spinosaurus', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit, Model: Spinosaurus', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/9/92/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Spinosaurus_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220807021957', 'grants the user the power to turn into a Spinosaurus, a large and powerful, semiaquatic, carnivorous theropod from the prehistoric era (considered to be the largest predatory dinosaur ever), as well as a hybrid between a Spinosaurus and human (or other) at will.', null, 'Page One', null, 3), 

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Pteranodon', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit, Model: Pteranodon', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/9/96/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Pteranodon_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220418123709', 'user of this fruit''s power can turn into a pteranodon: a large, flight-capable, predatory reptile from prehistory. Once transformed, they become able to fly at tremendous speed, covering large distances rapidly, and enjoy a significant boost to their overall physical abilities, as typical for a carnivorous Ancient Zoan user. Additionally, the full Beast Form as displayed by King is notably large, several times bigger than an average-sized human (though it is worth noting that King is already much larger than normal people in his normal form).', null, 'King', null, 3), 

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Brachiosaurus', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit, Model: Brachiosaurus', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/40/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Brachiosaurus_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/292?cb=20201004060008', 'allows the user to turn into a brachiosaurus, a very large and heavy-bodied sauropod dinosaur from the prehistoric era, granting them an immense boost to their size and bulk. Their size is comparable to that of a giant, as a fully-transformed Queen is shown to tower over Big Mom, who herself is extremely tall at over 8 meters.', null, 'Queen', null, 3),

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Pachycephalosaurus', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit, Model: Pachycephalosaurus', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/4b/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Pachycephalosaurus_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220227070532', 'fruit''s power is to turn into a full and hybrid version of a pachycephalosaurus: a bipedal, herbivorous dinosaur distinguished by its super-thick, durable skull roof. The Human-Beast Form already grants a significant increase in body size, with Ulti going from an ordinary height to over three times as tall, and her full Beast Form is even bigger, at least as large as her brother''s full spinosaurus form.', null, 'Ulti', null, 3), 

('Ryu Ryu no Mi, Model: Triceratops', 'Dragon-Dragon Fruit, Model: Triceratops', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/58/Ryu_Ryu_no_Mi%2C_Model_Triceratops_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220529042151', 'user of this Zoan can become a triceratops—a large, heavy-bodied, herbivorous dinosaur from prehistory—and assume a human-triceratops hybrid form.', null, 'Sasaki', null, 3),

('Zou Zou no Mi, Model: Mammoth', 'Eleph-Eleph Fruit, Model: Mammoth', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/d4/Zou_Zou_no_Mi%2C_Model_Mammoth_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20211212162937', 'allows the user to transform in full or hybrid mammoth at will. The full mammoth form granted by this fruit gives the user a massive frame, significantly increasing Jack''s already abnormal size. As an Ancient Zoan, this fruit grants the user greater strength than a normal Zoan.', null, 'Jack', null, 3),

('Kumo Kumo no Mi, Model: Rosamygale Grauvogeli', 'Spider-Spider Fruit, Model: Rosamygale Grauvogeli', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/7/7c/Kumo_Kumo_no_Mi_Model_Rosamygale_Grauvogeli_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220410040856', 'user of this Zoan can become a Rosamygale grauvogeli—a heavy-bodied, stout-legged mygalomorph spider from prehistoric times—as well as a human-spider hybrid.', null, 'Black Maria', null, 3),

('Neko Neko no Mi, Model: Saber Tiger', 'Cat-Cat Fruit, Model: Saber-Toothed Tiger', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/2/2a/Neko_Neko_no_Mi%2C_Model_Saber_Tiger_Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220623102748', 'user of this fruit''s power can turn into a ''saber-toothed tiger'' or Smilodon—a powerful, predatory big cat from prehistory that is characterized by its elongated, curved fangs on its upper jaw.', null, 'Who''s-Who', null, 3),

('Neko Neko no Mi, Model: Leopard', 'Cat-Cat Fruit, Model: Leopard', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/6/6e/Neko_Neko_no_Mi%2C_Model_Leopard_Human-Beast_Form.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220410054931', 'allows its user to transform into a leopard hybrid and a full leopard at will, making the user a Leopard Human (ヒョウ人間 Hyō Ningen).', null, 'Rob Lucci', null, 2),

('Hito Hito no Mi, Model: Daibutsu', 'Human-Human Fruit, Model: Buddha', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/4/45/Hito_Hito_no_Mi%2C_Model_Daibutsu_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20160818203351', 'allows the user to transform into a giant, living, golden Buddha, gaining an extreme boost in strength to match the increased size. In this form, Sengoku''s limbs grow out of proportion, giving him abnormally large arms and relatively tiny legs. His entire body takes on a solid gold hue (gray color in Gigant Battle); in addition to a full and hybrid transformation that are available to all Zoan Devil Fruit users, he can use palm thrusts to launch powerful shock waves.', null, 'Sengoku', null, 4),

('Hito Hito no Mi, Model: Onyudo', 'Human-Human Fruit, Model: Onyudo', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/d2/Onimaru_as_Gyukimaru.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20200712035243', 'allows its user to transform into an onyudo, a large monk yokai, at will.', null, 'Onimaru', null, 4),

('Zou Zou no Mi', 'Elephant-Elephant Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/c/c1/Funkfreed_Anime_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20160816232853', 'Funkfreed is Spandam''s sword, a unique weapon that ''ate'' the Zou Zou no Mi and became an Elephant Sword (象剣 Zōken). As such, he also serves as a pet and unofficial bodyguard for Spandam, compensating his master''s physical slightness.', null, 'Spandam''s sword, Funk Freed', null, 2),

('Unnamed Zoan Devil Fruit', 'Unnamed Zoan Devil Fruit', false, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/c/ca/Alpacacino_Anime_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/216?cb=20130129060954', 'a bazooka ''ate'' an unnamed Zoan Devil Fruit, allowing him to turn into a white alpaca with a metal band around his neck (a circular ring is attached to this) and his full body. His eyes turn red when he is taking his cannon position. He also has a purple crank on his left side. In his hybrid form, he also shows the handle of a bazooka.', null, 'Shuzo''s bazooka, Alpacacino', null, 2),

('Mogu Mogu no Mi', 'Mole-Mole Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/9/95/Mogu_Mogu_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20160814224126', 'allows its user to transform into a mole hybrid and a full mole at will, making the user a Mole Human (モグラ人間 Mogura Ningen).', null, 'Drophy aka Miss Merry Christmas', null, 2),

('Uma Uma no Mi', 'Horse-Horse Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/3/39/Uma_Uma_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220713111132', 'allows its user to transform into a horse hybrid and a full horse at will.', null, 'Gan Fall''s bird, Pierre', null, 2),

('Kame Kame no Mi', 'Turtle-Turtle Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/7/74/Kame_Kame_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20160120235204', 'allows the user to become a turtle hybrid and full turtle at will.', null, 'Pekoms', null, 2), 

('Tama Tama no Mi', 'Egg-Egg Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/a9/Tama_Tama_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20171203040745', 'turns the user''s body composition into that of an egg, which if cracked open will cause the user to regenerate into a stronger body that features more and more chicken-like features each time.', null, 'Tamago', null, 2),

('Moku Moku no Mi', 'Plume-Plume Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/8/8d/Moku_Moku_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest?cb=20200912191830', 'allows the user of this fruit to generate, manipulate, and become smoke. Like with most other Logia fruits, when hit, the user can simply use the fruit''s power to become smoke, thus absorbing the attack and remaining unharmed. Like some of the other Logia type Devil Fruits, it allows its user to ''fly'', by turning their body or the lower part of it into smoke, greatly enhancing their movement and speed.', null, 'Smoker the White Hunter', null, 5),

('Suna Suna no Mi', 'Sand-Sand Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/7/7d/Suna_Suna_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220408131752', 'allows the user to generate, control and transform into large quantities of sand. Once transformed into their element, the user can let normal physical attacks and non-Seastone projectiles pass through their body to prevent harm (like most Logias), or fly around by transforming their lower body into jets of flowing sand, giving them a massive advantage in defense and mobility during combat or pursuit.', null, 'Crocodile aka Mr. 0', null, 5),

('Mera Mera no Mi', 'Flame-Flame Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/8/8c/Mera_Mera_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20151123200729', 'allows the user to produce as well as become the element they control. In this case, the user is able to create, control, and become fire. With this in mind, the user can create devastating fire-based attacks and gain a high resistance towards most heat-based attacks. The flames can also be used to increase the force of physical attacks. The user is also able to avoid normal physical attacks by turning into fire and allowing the attack to harmlessly pass through their fiery body. Igniting oneself also has the added effect of burning an opponent if he or she had tried to physically harm the user.', null, 'Sabo','Portgas D. Ace', 5),

('Goro Goro no Mi', 'Rumble-Rumble Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/d/d2/Goro_Goro_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20181214005449', 'grants the power to create, control, and transform into lightning at will, making its user a Lightning Human (雷人間 Kaminari Ningen). Even for a Logia, this ability seems outstandingly potent, given the inherent destructiveness of lightning.', null, 'Enel', null, 5),

('Hie Hie no Mi', 'Ice-Ice Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/56/Hie_Hie_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20210322034024', 'allows its ability user to transform into the element of ice, as well as create and control it on a potentially massive scale, especially to freeze their surroundings. Particularly potent even by Logia standards.', null, 'Kuzan aka Aokiji', null, 5), 

('Yami Yami no Mi', 'Dark-Dark Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/f/f5/Yami_Yami_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20160123174331', 'allows the user to create, control, and transform into darkness. The darkness has strong gravitational properties and the user has an infinite amount of space inside of their elemental body.', null, 'Marshall D. Teach', null, 5),

('Pika Pika no Mi', 'Glint-Glint Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/6/66/Pika_Pika_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20110903091229', 'allows the user to create, control, and transform into light at will, turning the user into a Light Human (光人間 Hikari Ningen).It enables the user to move at the speed of light and transport themself by means of reflection.', null, 'Borsalino aka Admiral Kizaru', null, 5), 

('Magu Magu no Mi', 'Magma-Magma Fruit', true, null, 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/0/07/Magu_Magu_no_Mi_Infobox.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20220507164728', 'allows the user to become and produce magma to attack their opponents with. The intense heat can vaporize an iceberg instantly and boil seawater that the magma lands in.', null, 'Fleet Admiral Sakazuki, formerly known as Admiral Akainu', null, 5),

